2014年7月，宣布電影將於2015年8月21日上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2014/07/me-before-you-movie-release-date-2015-805337/ |title=WB Dates ‘Me Before You’ For August 2015 |publisher=Deadline |date=2014-07-16 |accessdate=2015-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725011437/http://deadline.com/2014/07/me-before-you-movie-release-date-2015-805337/ |archive-date=2015-07-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年5月，上映日延至2016年6月3日<ref>{{cite web |last=Busch |first=Anita |url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/me-before-you-release-date-thea-sharrock-1201427043/ |title=‘Me Before You’ Gets Release Date From Warner Bros. |publisher=Deadline |date=2015-05-14 |accessdate=2015-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724204627/http://deadline.com/2015/05/me-before-you-release-date-thea-sharrock-1201427043/ |archive-date=2015-07-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而2015年11月時，日期又提前改為2016年3月4日<ref>{{cite web |author=Anthony D'Alessandro |url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/me-before-you-emilia-clarke-jenna-coleman-march-release-date-1201620604/ |title=Emilia Clare ‘Me Before You’ Drama Opening In March 2016 |publisher=Deadline |date= |accessdate=2015-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114041612/http://deadline.com/2015/11/me-before-you-emilia-clarke-jenna-coleman-march-release-date-1201620604/ |archive-date=2015-11-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年1月再次推遲電影上映時間到2016年6月3日。

==迴響==
===票房===
我就要你好好的在北美的票房為5,624萬美元，在其他國家則高達1.52億美元，票房總收入為2.08億美金，而電影預算則是2,000萬美金<ref name=BOM />。

在北美地區，於2016年6月3日同日上映的電影除了我就要你好好的外，還有《{{link-en|流行巨星：永不停歇|Popstar: Never Stop Never Stopping}}》以及《[[忍者龜：破影而出|忍者龜：破影而出]]》一同競爭。《我就要你好好的》在首映周末預計能於2,704間影院開出1,500萬美金的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-sequel-to-top-box-office-but-faces-troubled-waters-ahead/ |title=‘Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles’ Sequel to Top Box Office, But Faces Troubled Waters Ahead |work=TheWrap.com |access-date=2016-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602170137/http://www.thewrap.com/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-sequel-to-top-box-office-but-faces-troubled-waters-ahead/ |archive-date=2016-06-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在星期四晚上的試映共得了140萬美金票房，首映當天票房則是780萬美金<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-me-before-you-pop-star-weekend-box-office-1201766674/|title=‘Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2’, ‘Me Before You’ Get Thursday Night Going – Box Office|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-06-03|accessdate=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604072625/http://deadline.com/2016/06/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-me-before-you-pop-star-weekend-box-office-1201766674/|archive-date=2016-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這部電影在首映周末票房排行榜上排名第三，票房總額為1,830萬美金，僅次於《忍者龜：破影而出》（3,530萬美金）與《X戰警：天啟》（2,230萬美金）<ref name="OpeningWeeknd">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-me-before-you-pop-star-weekend-box-office-1201766674/|title=‘NinjaTurtles 2’ Muscles Up On Saturday For OK Est. $35.3M Opening; ‘Me Before You’ Opens To $18.3M – Sunday AM B.O. Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-06-05|accessdate=2016-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604130702/http://deadline.com/2016/06/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-me-before-you-pop-star-weekend-box-office-1201766674/|archive-date=2016-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

