==爭議==
這部電影已遭受許多{{tsl|en|disability rights movement|身心障礙權益運動}}的反彈，因他們認為電影中隱藏了一個訊息，殘疾人是家人和照顧者的包袱，並宣稱此電影倡導與其讓他們成為負擔，不如提早結束自己生命<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2016/may/28/readers-editor-attitudes-changing-to-disability?CMP=share_btn_tw |title=Me Before You and Disability Article from The Guardian |website=The Guardian |accessdate=2016-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613190948/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2016/may/28/readers-editor-attitudes-changing-to-disability?CMP=share_btn_tw |archive-date=2016-06-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們認為電影鼓吹身心障礙者自殺，使他們的親人可以「活得沒有負擔」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.disabilitynewsservice.com/activists-protest-outside-premiere-of-disability-snuff-movie/ |title=Activists protest outside premiere of ‘disability snuff movie’ |website=DisabilityNewsService |accessdate=2016-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530192044/http://www.disabilitynewsservice.com/activists-protest-outside-premiere-of-disability-snuff-movie/ |archive-date=2016-05-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/voices/me-before-you-film-disability-sam-claflin-emilia-clarke-assisted-suicide-death-a7052716.html |title=Me Before You makes having a disability seem worse than death |website=The Independent |accessdate=2016-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531165051/http://www.independent.co.uk/voices/me-before-you-film-disability-sam-claflin-emilia-clarke-assisted-suicide-death-a7052716.html |archive-date=2016-05-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。#MeBeforeEuthanasia這項抵制電影的活動由英國殘疾名人{{tsl|en|Liz Carr|Liz Carr}}, Penny Pepper<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2016/jun/01/me-before-you-suggests-better-dead-than-disabled |title=We long to watch disabled characters like us. Instead we get Me Before You |website=The Guardian |accessdate=2016-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602063257/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2016/jun/01/me-before-you-suggests-better-dead-than-disabled |archive-date=2016-06-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，和{{tsl|en|Cherylee Houston|Cherylee Houston}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/coronation-streets-cherylee-houston-slams-8050717 |title=Cherylee Houston Article from The Mirror |website=TheMirror |accessdate=2016-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528124359/http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/coronation-streets-cherylee-houston-slams-8050717 |archive-date=2016-05-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/me-before-you-disability_us_575add48e4b00f97fba81730|title=The Disability Community Is Pissed AF About ‘Me Before You’|last=Elyse Wanshel Associate Editor|first=Good News|date=2016-06-10|website=The Huffington Post|access-date=2016-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622154541/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/me-before-you-disability_us_575add48e4b00f97fba81730|archive-date=2016-06-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及來自{{tsl|en|Not Dead Yet|Not Dead Yet}}在美國的活動家{{tsl|en|Dominick Evans|Dominick Evans}}和Emily Ladau所領導<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.self.com/trending/2016/05/why-some-disability-rights-activists-are-protesting-me-before-you/|title=Why Some Disability Rights Activists Are Protesting ‘Me Before You’ - SELF|access-date=2016-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630095031/http://www.self.com/trending/2016/05/why-some-disability-rights-activists-are-protesting-me-before-you/|archive-date=2016-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國的抗議活動發生在洛杉磯，紐約市，波士頓，科羅拉多州和德克薩斯州，亞特蘭大，巴爾的摩，康涅狄格州，羅切斯特，舊金山和全國各地。這部電影在澳大利亞也受到嚴重抗議<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/me-before-you-starring-gots-emilia-clarke-is-a-disability-snuff-movie-say-protesters-20160616-gpkqim.html|title=Me Before You, starring GoT's Emilia Clarke, is a 'disability snuff movie', say protesters|access-date=2016-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620063439/http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/me-before-you-starring-gots-emilia-clarke-is-a-disability-snuff-movie-say-protesters-20160616-gpkqim.html|archive-date=2016-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

